==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Solemnness
<hw>Sol"emn*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality of being
solemn; solemnity; impressiveness; gravity; <as>as, the
<ex>solemnness</ex> of public worship</as>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>solemness</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Solempne</ent>⟦br⟧
